<h1 class="csh-font-sans-bold">Como enviar uma sequência de e-mails após a compra ser aprovada na Hotmart</h1></div><div role="article" class="csh-article-content-text csh-article-content-text-large"><span data-type="|||" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-emphasis csh-font-sans-medium">* É importante lembrar que para isso você já deve ter feito a integração com o Hotmart no Bulldesk e já deve ter leads cadastrados na plataforma.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/>Caso ainda não tenha feito a integração com o Hotmart você deve ler o artigo que vou deixar <a href="https://ajuda.bulldesk.com.br/pt-br/article/como-integrar-o-bulldesk-com-a-hotmart-oeq7ai/" target="&lowbar;blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" role="link" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-link csh-markdown-link-text">aqui</a> e só depois voltar para este.<br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/>Caso você não tenha leads cadastrados na plataforma, você deve enviar um lead teste:<br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/lead-teste-homart_15d8nia.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/>Se você já estiver com estes fatores resolvidos:<br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="1" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Acesse sua conta no Bulldesk clicando <a href="https://app.bulldesk.com.br/login" target="&lowbar;blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" role="link" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-link csh-markdown-link-text">aqui</a>.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="2" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">No menu lateral a esquerda acesse a opção &quot;Leads&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_ndtam.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="3" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique em &quot;Filtre sua busca&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_a8w1g8.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="4" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique no botão &quot;Clique aqui&quot; para exibir filtros avançados.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_49ucbm.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="5" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique em &quot;Selecione o Filtro&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_1vtvywt.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="6" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Selecione a opção &quot;status&quot;, atenção ao fato de que não é a opção de &quot;Status&quot; do Bulldesk que aparece logo no início da lista de opções, a correta é a opção do status na Hotmart, ela deve aparecer lá no final da lista.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_48dnnz.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="7" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique no campo &quot;Regra&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_1v9iel7.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="8" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Escolha a opção &quot;É igual a&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_1o7tnw9.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="9" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">No campo ao lado escreva &quot;approved&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_1jevhe0.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="10" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique em &quot;+ Adicionar condição&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_1s0n2jf.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/>*Repita os passos 5, 6, 7 e 8 na linha que foi aberta abaixo do que você acabou de preencher. <br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_rsbkl4.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="11" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">No campo ao lado desta vez escreva &quot;completed&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_sk34zz.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="12" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique no campo localizado acima do botão verde.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_pjhsi8.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="13" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Escolha a opção &quot;Qualquer condição pode ser respeitada&quot;. Dessa forma, todos os leads que estiverem com status approved ou completed serão filtrados.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_5zpmwv.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="14" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique em &quot;Filtrar&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_1f9vwfr.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="15" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique em &quot;Salvar filtro como segmentação...&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_v6df7n.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="16" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Nomeie sua segmentação.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_135wcd4.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="17" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Salve sua segmentação.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_1fix9ky.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="||" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-emphasis csh-font-sans-medium">*Para a próxima parte você já deve ter os e-mails que deseja enviar criados, caso ainda não tenha passado por essa etapa, temos um artigo para te ajudar <a href="https://ajuda.bulldesk.com.br/pt-br/article/como-criar-um-novo-modelo-de-e-mail-1myygzf/" target="&lowbar;blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" role="link" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-link csh-markdown-link-text">aqui</a>.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="18" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">No menu lateral a esquerda acesse a opção &quot;Campanhas&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_aokvob.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="19" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique em &quot;Criar nova campanha&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_1iaj1t2.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="20" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Nomeie sua campanha, escolha a opção de &quot;campanha automatizada&quot; e clique em continuar.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_f9pqlh.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="21" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique no botão &quot;+&quot; para definir a regra da sua campanha.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_y91pjq.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="22" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique em &quot;Escolher regra&quot; na opção &quot;Leads novos ou atualizados na segmentação&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_2g6iav.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="23" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Escolha a segmentação que você salvou na etapa 17 e clique em &quot;Salvar&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_1jc9isc.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="24" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Arraste a tela para baixo e clique no &quot;+&quot; para escolher o que acontecerá com os leads dessa segmentação que você selecionou.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_1kcpctj.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="25" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Clique em &quot;Escolher ação&quot; na opção de &quot;Enviar e-mail&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_ce2m60.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="26" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Escolha o e-mail que você criou, deixe para ser executado 0 segundos após a ação anterior e clique em &quot;Salvar&quot;.</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/captura-de-tela-2021-04-07-as-_1qud63t.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="||" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-emphasis csh-font-sans-medium">*Se desejar enviar uma sequência de e-mails repita as etapas 24, 25 e 26 apenas alterando o tempo após a ação anterior.</span><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-line csh-article-content-separate csh-article-content-separate-top"></span><p class="csh-article-content-updated csh-text-wrap csh-font-sans-light">Atualizado em: 08/04/2021</p><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-line csh-article-content-separate csh-article-content-separate-bottom"></span></div></article><section data-has-answer="false" role="none" class="csh-article-rate"><div class="csh-article-rate-ask csh-text-wrap"><p class="csh-article-rate-title csh-font-sans-medium">Este artigo foi útil?</p><ul><li><a href="#" role="button" aria-label="Sim" onclick="CrispHelpdeskArticle.answer_feedback(true); return false;" class="csh-button csh-button-grey csh-button-small csh-font-sans-medium">Sim</a></li><li><a href="#" role="button" aria-label="Não" onclick="CrispHelpdeskArticle.answer_feedback(false); return false;" class="csh-button csh-button-grey csh-button-small csh-font-sans-medium">Não</a></li></ul></div><div data-is-open="false" class="csh-article-rate-feedback-wrap"><div data-had-error="false" class="csh-article-rate-feedback-container"><form action="https://ajuda.bulldesk.com.br/pt-br/article/como-enviar-uma-sequencia-de-e-mails-apos-a-compra-ser-aprovada-na-hotmart-1ny0hkx/feedback/" method="post" onsubmit="CrispHelpdeskArticle.send_feedback_comment(this); return false;" data-is-locked="false" class="csh-article-rate-feedback"><p class="csh-article-rate-feedback-title csh-font-sans-bold">Compartilhe seu feedback</p><textarea name="feedback_comment" cols="1" rows="1" maxlength="200" placeholder="Explique brevemente o que você acha deste artigo. Poderemos entrar em contato com você." onkeyup="CrispHelpdeskArticle.type_feedback_comment(event)" class="csh-article-rate-feedback-field csh-font-sans-regular"></textarea><div class="csh-article-rate-feedback-actions"><button type="submit" role="button" aria-label="Enviar minha opinião" data-action="send" class="csh-button csh-button-accent csh-font-sans-medium">Enviar minha opinião</button><a href="#" role="button" aria-label="Cancelar" onclick="CrispHelpdeskArticle.cancel_feedback_comment(); return false;" data-action="cancel" class="csh-button csh-button-grey csh-font-sans-medium">Cancelar</a></div></form